text: Jasmine Cephas Jones (born July 21, 1989) is an American actress and singer. She is best known for originating the dual roles of Peggy Schuyler and Maria Reynolds in the 2015 Broadway musical Hamilton. On December 24, 2018, Cephas Jones became engaged to Hamilton original Broadway cast member Anthony Ramos. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from New York City Category:American movie actors Category:American stage actors Category:American television actors Category:Singers from New York City
